data.description:
*** HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT *** 

Nestled in a quiet Edmond cul-de-sac, and backing up to serene water views - your dream home awaits you. 
Step inside your inviting foyer that greets you with an abundance of natural light and cathedral ceilings. This stunning 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home offers so much space, and flexibility. The heart of the home is a chef's delight, with a well-appointed kitchen that features granite counter tops, modern stainless-steel appliances and plenty of storage. Open to the kitchen is the family room with vaulted ceilings and wood beam accents. Which are in great company with the gorgeous stone fireplace. Your large primary suite boasts private patio access, his/hers closets and an on-suite spa like bathroom that is located on the main level of the home. Along with your study and cute half bath. Upstairs the spacious bedrooms and baths provide ample and cozy spaces. Your backyard sanctuary beckons with tree lined, lake views. The outdoor fireplace adds warmth and ambiance making it a go-to spot for relaxation. Located in the sought-after community of Lakeview at Coffee Creek and zoned for the highly regarded Edmond School district. This home combines tranquility and convenience. Shopping, dining and entertainment are just minutes away. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home and experience the lifestyle you have been dreaming of!
